  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the air fryer to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Season the beef short ribs with salt and black pepper.",
    "Add the beef short ribs to the air fryer basket and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Remove the beef short ribs from the air fryer and set aside.",
    "In a large Dutch oven, heat the olive oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the carrots, onions, and celery to the pot and cook until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Add the garlic, thyme, and bay leaves to the pot and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the beef broth, red wine, and dark brown soft sugar to the pot and bring to a boil.",
    "Return the beef short ribs to the pot and simmer for 2 hours.",
    "Serve the beef short ribs hot, garnished with fresh parsley and thyme if desired.",
    "Remove the bay leaves before serving."
